extends base

block content 
  main
    .hero
      .hero__text-box
        h1.hero__heading "DUBAI'S BOOMING HOTEL INDUSTRY"
        h2.hero__sub-heading EXPOSED
    div
      h2.heading How this works
      .how-it-works__timeline
        ol.how-it-works__list
          li.how-it-works__item
            span.how-it-works__number 1
            .how-it-works__text-box
              h3.how-it-works__heading Share your story
              p.how-it-works__description
                | You fill in the form in contact, providing your story with any contracts
                | and bank statements.
          li.how-it-works__item
            span.how-it-works__number 2
            .how-it-works__text-box
              h3.how-it-works__heading
                | The first group asks us for your info
              p.how-it-works__description
                | The first group asks us for contact info linked to each story.
          li.how-it-works__item
            span.how-it-works__number 3
            .how-it-works__text-box
              h3.how-it-works__heading
                | The first group refunds your money
              p.how-it-works__description
                | You receive the money that is shown on all statements. Undoing the financial impact.
          li.how-it-works__item
            span.how-it-works__number 4
            .how-it-works__text-box
              h3.how-it-works__heading
                | You confirm your refund was received
              p.how-it-works__description
                | You email us with the statements proving your refund. 


          li.how-it-works__item
            span.how-it-works__number 5
            .how-it-works__text-box
              h3.how-it-works__heading
                | We remove your story from our list
              p.how-it-works__description
                | Win Win. You get your money back and they get less bad publicity.
        p.how-it-works__conclusion
          | With this system, we can help as many people as possible get their
          | money back. <br />The more stories we have, the more pressure we can
          | put on the first group to do the right thing.
      .break-line
      .our-goal
        h2.heading Why We're Doing This
        p.our-goal__text
          | This situation is unfair and people have been taken advantage of. You trusted The First Group with your money, 
          | your time, and your dreams of building something in Dubai. They made big promises, 
          | showed you fancy projections, and then... nothing went as planned.
        p.our-goal__text
          | The problem? When you try to Google them or search for reviews, there's barely anything 
          | there. No warnings. No red flags. Just their polished marketing. Meanwhile, real people 
          | are losing real money, and nobody can find out about it until it's too late.
        p.our-goal__text
          | That's where this site comes in. We're creating a searchable record of actual 
          | victim experiences backed by real documents, real contracts, and real bank statements. 
          | When someone Googles "The First Group" or "First Group Dubai reviews," they'll find this (hopefully). 
          | They'll see your story. They'll know what really happened.
        p.our-goal__text
          | But here's the other part: we genuinely want to help you get your money back. By putting 
          | pressure on The First Group through public accountability, we're hoping they'll do the 
          | right thing and issue refunds. The more stories we have, the harder it becomes for them 
          | to ignore.
        p.our-goal__text
          | We're exposing their tactics, their communication patterns, and the red flags others 
          | should watch for. If we can stop even one person from going through what you went through, 
          | this will have been worth it.
        p.our-goal__note
          | ALL STORIES ARE PUBLISHED ANONYMOUSLY. YOUR PERSONAL INFO STAYS PRIVATE.
        a.our-goal__link(href="https://xodo.com/redact-pdf", target="_blank")
          | Need to hide sensitive details in your documents? Use this free redaction tool ➣➣

    .break-line
    ul.page-links
      a.page-links__link(href="/how-they-work") How they work 
      a.page-links__link(href="/stories") Stories
      a.page-links__link(href="/contact") Contact 